507
00:47:01,053 --> 00:47:03,005
Tudo num dia.

508
00:47:03,554 --> 00:47:05,546
Numa noite.

509
00:47:05,547 --> 00:47:08,386
Vai ser de noite, não de dia.

510
00:47:08,771 --> 00:47:11,133
Noite, sim, noite.

511
00:47:12,626 --> 00:47:14,140
Tu és lento?

512
00:47:14,141 --> 00:47:16,093
Ouve, Proteus.

513
00:47:16,094 --> 00:47:19,345
